### 获取用户列表 (需要管理员token)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/user/list
token: admin_token_valid
Content-Type: application/json

### 搜索用户
GET http://localhost:5000/api/user/list?keyword=张
token: admin_token_valid
Content-Type: application/json

### 新增用户
POST http://localhost:5000/api/user/add
token: admin_token_valid
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "19987654321",
  "nickname": "新用户",
  "gender": "男",
  "address": "天河区",
  "role": "普通用户",
  "status": "启用"
}

### 编辑用户
POST http://localhost:5000/api/user/edit
token: admin_token_valid
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "U20260101000003",
  "nickname": "王五（已修改）",
  "address": "番禺区"
}

### 修改用户状态
POST http://localhost:5000/api/user/changeStatus
token: admin_token_valid
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "U20260101000005",
  "status": "启用"
}

### 删除用户
POST http://localhost:5000/api/user/delete
token: admin_token_valid
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "U20260101000005"
}

### 无权限测试 (普通用户token)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/user/list
token: user_token_valid
Content-Type: application/json

### 无效token测试
GET http://localhost:5000/api/user/list
token: invalid_token
Content-Type: application/json